T1  - An interpretation of unequal exchange from Prebisch-Singer to Emmanuel
AU  - Bacha, Edmar L.
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 5
IS  - 4
SP  - 319
EP  - 330
PY  - 1978
DA  - 1978/12/01/
